@{FG Highlight}Art Expression 1.0:@{FG Text}
- The leading Amiga illustration program.
- Compatible with all major formats: IFF DR2D, AE EPS, Illustrator EPS, Aegis Draw, ProDraw.
- Bend text on a curved path, warp text in shapes.
- Draw basic shapes and complex paths.
- Edit paths: add, deleted, join, split and align points.
- Compatible with all PostScript Type 1 fonts.
- Comes with BME trace.
- Suggested retail price: $249.95.

@{FG Highlight}Graphic Library:@{FG Text}
- Innovative new clip art in Adobe Illustrator EPS format.
- 3D Flags of the World, 190 illustrations: $67
- Amiga Computer Art,    75 illustrations:  $67

@{FG Highlight}Serials Typecollection@{FG Text}
- 1000 Fonts on a CD-ROM for only $499.
- PostScript Type 1 and TrueType, Mac and PC (Amiga) formats.
- ISO 9660 format. It can be used on Amiga, Macintosh and MS-DOS computers.
- Also available on Syquest cartridges.

@{FG Highlight}PageStream3@{FG Text}
- The world's best desktop publishing program.
- Compatible with PostScript, Compugraphic and Soft-Logik fonts.
- Place text and graphics.
- Long document publishing.
- Professional color publishing:
  - spot colors with PANTONE® color support
  - color separations with trapping and plate control.
- Gradient fills, merged paths, edit points.
- Print to dot matrix, ink jet and laser printers.
- Output to plotters and imagesetters.
- Suggested retail price: $395.

